attributes.name: ecm_inv_scan.linux.configuration_files.nrpe
attributes.value:
log_facility=daemon
pid_file=varrunnrpenrpe.pid
server_port=5666
nrpe_user=nrpe
nrpe_group=nrpe
allowed_hosts=127.0.0.1,185.49.176.16028,185.49.176.19226,10.48.202.84,2001:9d0:2:10f::b931:b0c8
dont_blame_nrpe=1
debug=0
command_timeout=60
connection_timeout=300

ssl_client_certs=2
ssl_version=TLSv1+
ssl_cipher_list=ALL:!aNULL:!eNULL:!SSLv2:!LOW:!EXP:!RC4:!MD5:@STRENGTH
ssl_cacert_file=etcnagiosnrpe.ssl.ca-crt
ssl_cert_file=etcnagiosnrpe.ssl.crt
ssl_privatekey_file=etcnagiosnrpe.ssl.key

command[check_process]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_procs $ARG1$
command[check_users]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_users $ARG1$
command[check_load]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_load $ARG1$
command[check_disk]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_disk $ARG1$
command[check_mem]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_mem $ARG1$
command[check_cpu]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_cpu $ARG1$
command[check_mailq]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_mailq $ARG1$
command[check_dmesg]=usrlib64nagiospluginscheck_dmesg.sh $ARG1$

include_dir=etcnrpe.d
